{
  "title": "Slice Keyboard Gestures",
  "parts": [
    {
      "type": "html",
      "content": "<h1 id=\"slice-keyboard-gestures\">Slice Keyboard Gestures</h1>\n<p>Slice Keyboard supports several gestures to make typing faster and more fluid.</p>\n<h2 id=\"capitalization-gesture\">Capitalization Gesture</h2>\n<p>Capitalize any key by pressing and flinging on any key.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/slice-keyboard/tutorial/nexus7-tutorial-cap-cropped.png\" alt=\"Capitalization Gesture\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"space-gesture\">Space Gesture</h2>\n<p>Add a space by pressing a Home Key and flinging to the Right.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/slice-keyboard/tutorial/nexus10-tutorial-space-cropped.png\" alt=\"Space Gesture\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"delete-gesture\">Delete Gesture</h2>\n<p>Delete a character by pressing a Home Key and flinging to the Left</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/slice-keyboard/tutorial/nexus10-tutorial-delete-cropped.png\" alt=\"Delete Gesture\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"hand-switch-gesture\">Hand Switch Gesture</h2>\n<p>When typing with one hand switch the keys to opposite hand&#39;s keys by pressing a Home Key and flinging Up. The Swap Hand Gesture will work only when typing with one hand.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/slice-keyboard/tutorial/nexus7-tutorial-swap-hand-cropped.png\" alt=\"Hand Switch Gesture\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"display-preview-mode\">Display Preview Mode</h2>\n<p>Preview Mode displays all of the keys at once. To open Preview Mode swipe in from the left or right edges of the screen.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/slice-keyboard/tutorial/nexus10-tutorial-preview-close-cropped.png\" alt=\"Preview Mode\"></p>\n"
    }
  ],
